Start
Declare variables t,n,i
Declare integers Basic Salary, HRA and DA
Initilize the value of Basic Salary
If Basic Salary is less than 1500
HRA = 10% of Base Salary
DA = 90% of Base Salary
Else
Basic Salary is greaterthan or equal to1500
HRA = 500
DA = 98% of Base Salary
Print the value of HRA and DA
End
